{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.83\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">亞薩的詩歌。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">求主敗敵</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>上帝啊，求你不要靜默！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">上帝啊，求你不要閉口，不要不作聲！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>因為你的仇敵喧嚷，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">恨你的抬起頭來。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>他們同謀奸詐要害你的百姓，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">彼此商議要害你所保護的人。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>他們說：「來吧，我們將他們除滅，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">使他們不再成國！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">使<span class=\"pn\">以色列</span>的名不再被人記念！」</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>他們同心商議，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">彼此結盟，要抵擋你；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.6\" class=\"v6\">6</sup>他們就是住帳棚的<span class=\"pn\">以東</span>和<span class=\"pn\">以實瑪利</span>人，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\"><span class=\"pn\">摩押</span>和<span class=\"pn\">夏甲</span>人，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v7\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.7\" class=\"v7\">7</sup><span class=\"pn\">迦巴勒</span>、<span class=\"pn\">亞捫</span>、</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v7\"><span class=\"pn\">亞瑪力</span>、<span class=\"pn\">非利士</span>和<span class=\"pn\">推羅</span>的居民。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v8\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.8\" class=\"v8\">8</sup><span class=\"pn\">亞述</span>也與他們聯合，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v8\">作<span class=\"pn\">羅得</span>子孫的幫手。（細拉）</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v9\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.9\" class=\"v9\">9</sup>求你待他們，如待<span class=\"pn\">米甸</span>，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v9\">如在<span class=\"pn\">基順河</span>待<span class=\"pn\">西西拉</span>和<span class=\"pn\">耶賓</span>一樣。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v10\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.10\" class=\"v10\">10</sup>他們在<span class=\"pn\">隱‧多珥</span>滅亡，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v10\">成了地上的糞土。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v11\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.11\" class=\"v11\">11</sup>求你使他們的貴族像<span class=\"pn\">俄立</span>和<span class=\"pn\">西伊伯</span>，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v11\">使他們的王子都像<span class=\"pn\">西巴</span>和<span class=\"pn\">撒慕拿</span>。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v12\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.12\" class=\"v12\">12</sup>因為他們說：「我們要得上帝的住處，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v12\">作自己的產業。」</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v13\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.13\" class=\"v13\">13</sup>我的上帝啊，求你使他們像旋風中的塵土，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v13\">如風前的碎秸。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v14\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.14\" class=\"v14\">14</sup>火怎樣焚燒樹林，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v14\">火焰怎樣燒著山嶺，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v15\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.15\" class=\"v15\">15</sup>求你也照樣用狂風追趕他們，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v15\">用暴雨恐嚇他們。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v16\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.16\" class=\"v16\">16</sup>耶和華啊，求你使他們滿面羞恥，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v16\">好叫他們尋求你的名！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v17\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.17\" class=\"v17\">17</sup>願他們永遠羞愧驚惶！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v17\">願他們慚愧滅亡！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v18\"><sup id=\"Ps.83.18\" class=\"v18\">18</sup>願他們認識你的名是耶和華，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v18\">惟獨你是掌管全地的至高者！</span></p>\n</div>\n"}